text-unit.text:
For equations that seem impossible to break over several lines, two options are available. First, an experimental package for setting equations that span two columns, asmewide.sty, can be loaded, although that code may require hand-fitting around floats and page breaks (see the examples in [



  23



]). Second, a new page can be started in one-column mode, then returning to two-column mode:

