text-unit.text:
Note that selecting bold-face italic depends on the engine: with pdf

 TEX

, do 

 \bm{..}

; with Lua

 LATEX

, do 

 \symbfit{..}

. But for both engines, you can get upright letters, as used in the text font, using 

 \mathbf{..}

 or with 

 \textbf{..}

